          class="float-left mr-1.5 h-5 w-5 rounded-sm bg-[url(https://raw.githubusercontent.com/georgevgs/gv-portfolio/main/public/favicon.svg)] bg-cover md:-mt-0.5 md:h-6 md:w-6"
        ></span>
        Made by <a
          class="vagdas-link font-bold"
